+
+All notable changes to this project are documented here.
+
+The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
+and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).
+While pre-1.0, breaking platform changes increment the minor version.
+
+## [0.2.0] - 2026-05-22
+
+### Changed
+
+- **Breaking — platform migration.** Upgraded the core stack: Next.js 14 → 16, React 18 → 19, and Tailwind CSS 3 → 4. Contributors must reinstall dependencies (`npm install`) after pulling; the new major versions of these frameworks have their own breaking changes that affect local development and the build.
+- Tailwind 4 now loads via `@tailwindcss/postcss` and a CSS-first `@import "tailwindcss"` entry point (replacing the `@tailwind base/components/utilities` directives and the standalone `autoprefixer` PostCSS plugin).
+- Upgraded tooling to TypeScript 6 and ESLint 10 (with matching `typescript-eslint` and `eslint-plugin-react-hooks` releases).
+- Bumped the Google Gemini SDK (`@google/generative-ai`) to 0.24.x.
+
+## [0.1.0]
+
+- Initial scaffold: design system, marketing/brand/dashboard routes, and the funder-desk dashboard module with mocked data and integrations.
+

